changelog
----------

02/7/09 - Stable "End User Release" (0.0.2.6)
	  + aiml parser now subclasses qthread
	  + execution is qprocess'd now
	  + gui fixes
	  + more braindata++
	  + new progressbar (Plasma::Slider)
	  + more work on aimlparser

01/12/09 - Stable "Qt4 Release" (0.0.2.5)
	  + proper execution handling (not finished)
	  + more brainpower
	  + pure qt4 code now - 20% speed increase in loading time
		(no more q3ptrlist/q3valuelist thx to 
		asraniel from #plasma)
	  + kde4 compliancy tweaks
	  + /usr/share/apps/openbrain dir now instead of ugly hacks

12/28/08 - Bug Fix release (0.0.2-3)
	  + fixed <br> tags
	  + fixed umlaut-y symbol error <- for now :( #swap to QFile
	  + cleaned and organized code
	  + QString filtering via void works now (for thinkOf();)
	  + more AIML modifications

12/27/08 - First plasmoid release (0.0.2-2)
